This paper is primarily focused on energy-efficient data center networking, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses traffic engineering and optimization, which could fall under the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), systems and control (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, since the paper's main focus is on networking, cs.NI is the most likely category, followed by cs.DC and cs.SY.
